# The harness calls Claude directly through the Anthropic API (not the Vercel AI
# Gateway), so usage bills to your Anthropic organisation / enterprise account.
#
# Local development: get a key from the Anthropic Console (API keys) and paste it
# here in a file named `.env.local`.
#
# On Vercel: set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY in the project's environment variables.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional per-stage model overrides (bare Anthropic model IDs), e.g.:
# HARNESS_MODEL_UNDERSTAND=claude-opus-4-8
# HARNESS_MODEL_GENERATE=claude-sonnet-5
